OL,3,CRider dies in crash at North West 200
OL,5,F"The session was immediately red
OL,6,Fflagged and emergency services
OL,7,Fattended the scene but unfortunately
OL,8,Fthe rider succumbed to his injuries.
OL,10,F"The family have given their approval
OL,11,Ffor the event to continue but have
OL,12,Frequested that the rider not be named
OL,13,Fat this time.
OL,15,F"Coleraine and District Motor Club,
OL,16,Fthe organisers of the races, offer our
OL,17,Fsincere condolences to the family and
OL,18,Fteam."
